This is the buildsystem for the Lion 3rd Generation based on the OpenWrt Linux distribution.

Please use "make menuconfig" to configure the toolchain and firmware.

Requirements:
gcc, binutils, bzip2, flex, python, perl, make,find, grep, diff, unzip, gawk, getopt, subversion, libz-dev and libc headers.

Run "./scripts/feeds update -a" to get all the latest package definitions
defined in feeds.conf / feeds.conf.default respectively
and "./scripts/feeds install -a" to install symlinks of all of them into
package/feeds/.

